#

Garlic Tomato Bruschetta

15 min
$8.5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVegan

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerItalianEasy

Description

A delightful appetizer featuring toasted bread topped with a fresh tomato and garlic mixture, perfect for any gathering.

Ingredients

  • baguette: 1
  • roma tomatoes: 3
  • fresh basil leaves: 1/2 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
